<p>77. Other institutions that 
have played a role include the 
United Nations, the Office of 
the High Representative, the 
Organization for Security and 
Cooperation in Europe, the 
International Committee of 
the Red Cross, the European 
Union and others. These 
organizations should continue 
to work on the problem of 
