<p>Other actors: 
One of the main challenges currently faced for the Missing Persons file to progress 
is the lack of new information. Avenues such as plea agreements, mitigating 
circumstances as well as  dialogue with stakeholders whose archives may 
potentially contribute to the clarification of the fate and whereabouts of missing 
persons, should be further explored.  
 
