<p>sentencing or imposing adequate sanctions for the gravest violations of 
international humanitarian law. The State of BiH has undertaken this obligation 
not only by ratifying the relevant international conventions strictly providing for 
this obligation, but also by the guarantees it has offered in taking over the cases 
transferred to BiH by The Hague Tribunal from its jurisdiction. [&#8230;] 
